name: "Sigh" Cake - Carrot
description: @Sugartivi | Dear art collector, sometimes the best way to deal when things are not going our way - is to really feel the disappointment. This is hard but it lets us move onward. This carrot Sigh cake has traditional cream cheese frosting and spicy layers of carrot cake inside. Many people find carrot cake boring or disappointing as far as cakes go - but I do not.
